<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - E-Commerce</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />

    @* ✅ Render page-specific styles *@
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Styles", required: false)

    @*
    ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    ✅ FIX: Navbar & dropdown z-index override.
    Đặt SAU @RenderSectionAsync("Styles") để luôn thắng bất kỳ
    page CSS nào (kể cả !important cùng specificity — last wins).

    Nguyên nhân lỗi: Shop/Index.cshtml có rule
      .navbar { position:relative !important; z-index:1 !important }
    để fix aurora blob che footer. Rule đó kéo navbar từ z-index 1020
    xuống 1, khiến dropdown-menu (z-index 1000 theo Bootstrap nhưng
    scoped trong stacking context z-index:1 của navbar) bị các element
    khác trên trang đè lên.

    Fix: Khôi phục z-index đúng cho navbar + dropdown LUÔN LUÔN,
    dù page nào đang render.
    ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    *@
    <style>
        /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
               GLOBAL NAVBAR + DROPDOWN UI OVERHAUL
               - Z-index fix (dropdown không bị trang che)
               - Modern glassmorphism dropdown panel
               - Animated slide-in
               - Item hover gradient
               - Navbar pill toggle & brand polish
            ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

        /* ── 0. Variables ── */
        :root {
            --nav-g: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 60%, #ec4899 100%);
            --nav-g-soft: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,70,229,.08) 0%, rgba(124,58,237,.06) 100%);
            --nav-accent: #7c3aed;
            --nav-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(79,70,229,.18), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
            --nav-r: 16px;
        }

        /* ── 1. Z-index fix (always wins over page CSS) ── */

        /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
               ✅ FIX ĐỊNH GỐC: TẠI SAO DROPDOWN BỊ CHE?
               ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
               Nguyên nhân THỰC SỰ: các page dùng:
                 • filter: blur() trên aurora blobs → tạo stacking context mới
                 • transform-style: preserve-3d trên hero img → idem
                 • backdrop-filter, opacity, transform trên cards → idem
               Những stacking context này nổi lên ROOT context, chen ngang
               với navbar. Dù navbar có z-index 1050, dropdown (nằm trong
               navbar's stacking context) vẫn bị các page element đè lên
               nếu chúng được paint SAU navbar theo DOM order.

               GIẢI PHÁT ĐÚNG: isolation: isolate trên <main>
               ── Tạo một stacking context CÔ LẬT cho toàn bộ page content ──
               • Mọi stacking context bên trong main (filter, transform, z-index
                 bất kỳ) đều bị "nhốt" hoàn toàn trong hộp này
               • Hộp này ở z-index: 0 trong root
               • Navbar ở z-index: 1050 → LUÔN trên main → dropdown KHÔNG BAO
                 GIỜ bị che nữa, dù page có bao nhiêu filter/transform đi nữa
            ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

        /* ── 1a. NHỐT tất cả page stacking contexts vào isolated box ── */
        main[role="main"],
        main.pb-3 {
            position: relative !important;
            z-index: 0 !important;
            isolation: isolate !important;
        }

        /* ── 1b. Navbar: sticky, luôn trên main (0) ── */
        .navbar, nav.navbar, header > nav, header nav.navbar {
            position: sticky !important;
            top: 0 !important;
            z-index: 1050 !important;
        }

            /* ── 1c. Dropdown: cao nhất trong navbar's stacking context ── */
            .dropdown-menu,
            .navbar .dropdown-menu,
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu {
                z-index: 9999 !important;
            }

        /* ── 1d. Header wrapper: safety net ── */
        body > header {
            position: relative !important;
            z-index: 1050 !important;
        }

        /* ── 2. Navbar bar polish ── */
        nav.navbar {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.92) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(180%) !important;
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(180%) !important;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.12) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 24px rgba(79,70,229,.08), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04) !important;
            padding-top: 10px !important;
            padding-bottom: 10px !important;
        }

        /* Brand */
        .navbar-brand {
            background: var(--nav-g) !important;
            -webkit-background-clip: text !important;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent !important;
            background-clip: text !important;
            font-weight: 900 !important;
            letter-spacing: -.5px !important;
            transition: opacity .2s !important;
        }

            .navbar-brand:hover {
                opacity: .8 !important;
            }

            .navbar-brand i {
                -webkit-text-fill-color: #4f46e5 !important;
                color: #4f46e5 !important;
            }

        /* Nav links */
        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            color: #334155 !important;
            padding: 8px 14px !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            transition: background .2s, color .2s !important;
            position: relative !important;
        }

            .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover,
            .navbar-nav .nav-link:focus {
                color: var(--nav-accent) !important;
                background: var(--nav-g-soft) !important;
            }

        /* ── 3. Dropdown TOGGLE button ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-toggle {
            display: inline-flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 8px !important;
            background: var(--nav-g) !important;
            color: #fff !important;
            border-radius: 50px !important;
            padding: 8px 18px !important;
            font-weight: 700 !important;
            font-size: 13.5px !important;
            border: none !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(79,70,229,.28) !important;
            transition: all .25s !important;
            letter-spacing: .1px !important;
        }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-toggle::after {
                margin-left: 4px !important;
                border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,.8) !important;
                transition: transform .3s !important;
            }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-toggle:hover,
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-toggle:focus {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(79,70,229,.40) !important;
                transform: translateY(-1px) !important;
                color: #fff !important;
            }
        /* Arrow rotate when open */
        .navbar-nav .nav-item.show > .dropdown-toggle::after {
            transform: rotate(180deg) !important;
        }

        /* ── 4. Dropdown PANEL ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu {
            min-width: 220px !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            border: none !important;
            border-radius: var(--nav-r) !important;
            box-shadow: var(--nav-shadow) !important;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.97) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%) !important;
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%) !important;
            overflow: hidden !important;
            /* ✅ KHÔNG dùng display:block trick — Bootstrap JS tự quản lý show/hide */
            /* Animation chỉ apply khi Bootstrap thêm class .show */
        }

            /* ✅ Animation: chạy đúng lúc Bootstrap thêm .show — không can thiệp toggle */
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu.show {
                animation: navDropIn .22s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) forwards !important;
            }
        @@keyframes navDropIn {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(.96);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
        }

        }

        /* Remove old show rules — no longer needed */
        .navbar-nav .nav-item.show > .dropdown-menu {
            /* intentionally empty — Popper+fixed strategy handles positioning */
        }

        /* Panel — gradient header bar */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu::before {
            content: '' !important;
            display: block !important;
            height: 4px !important;
            background: var(--nav-g) !important;
            border-radius: var(--nav-r) var(--nav-r) 0 0 !important;
        }

        /* Inner padding */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu li:not(:first-child) {
            padding: 0 8px !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu li:first-child {
            padding: 0 !important;
        }

        /* ── 5. Dropdown ITEMS ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-item {
            display: flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 10px !important;
            padding: 10px 16px !important;
            font-size: 13.5px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            color: #334155 !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            margin: 2px 0 !important;
            transition: background .18s, color .18s, transform .18s !important;
            position: relative !important;
        }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-item:hover,
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-item:focus {
                background: var(--nav-g-soft) !important;
                color: var(--nav-accent) !important;
                transform: translateX(3px) !important;
            }
            /* Dot accent */
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-item::before {
                content: '' !important;
                width: 6px !important;
                height: 6px !important;
                border-radius: 50% !important;
                background: var(--nav-g) !important;
                opacity: 0 !important;
                flex-shrink: 0 !important;
                transition: opacity .18s !important;
            }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-item:hover::before,
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-item:focus::before {
                opacity: 1 !important;
            }

        /* ── 6. Divider ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-divider {
            margin: 6px 16px !important;
            border-color: rgba(124,58,237,.12) !important;
            border-top-width: 1.5px !important;
            opacity: 1 !important;
        }

        /* ── 7. Logout button ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu form button.dropdown-item {
            width: 100% !important;
            text-align: left !important;
            background: none !important;
            border: none !important;
            cursor: pointer !important;
        }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu form button.dropdown-item:hover {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239,68,68,.08), rgba(251,113,133,.05)) !important;
                color: #dc2626 !important;
            }

                .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu form button.dropdown-item:hover::before {
                    background: #ef4444 !important;
                    opacity: 1 !important;
                }

        /* ── 8. Spacing ── */
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu > li:last-child {
            padding-bottom: 8px !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu > li:nth-child(2) {
            padding-top: 6px !important;
        }

        /* ── 9. Wishlist badge ── */
        #wishlistBadge {
            font-size: 0.6em !important;
            padding: 2px 5px !important;
            min-width: 18px !important;
            line-height: 1.4 !important;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(220,38,38,.35) !important;
        }

        /* ── 10. Mobile ── */
        @@media (max-width: 991px) {
            .navbar-nav .dropdown-toggle

        {
            width: 100% !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            justify-content: space-between !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            margin-bottom: 4px !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(79,70,229,.12) !important;
            margin-top: 4px !important;
            /* no transform override needed — .show animation handles it */
        }

            .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu.show {
                animation: none !important; /* no animation on mobile collapse */
            }

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
